title: À-Bas-Le-Ciel vs. Ask Yourself! Racism, Veganism & the Meaning of Life!
description:
Some people will rush to ask, "Did we talk about racism?"  Or even, "Did I confront him about Cory McCarthy / Tara McCarthy?"  Yes, we talked about all that of those things at length (and more!), but there was nothing confrontational about it: we had a totally productive conversation.

THIS IS JUST A PROMO.  Maybe it'll take 12 hours to upload the "real" video, we'll see.  However, I don't mean to mislead you: the video I'm uploading now is just my set of reflections after the conversation wrapped up.  We DID NOT record the original conversation, partly because it transpired between 3:00 AM and 8:00 AM in Isaac's time-zone!  He said he wasn't feeling too sharp, but, in fact, he was exceedingly sharp throughout the entire dialogue.
